<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include("partials/header", { title: "Career Quiz - Career Advisor" }) %>
</head>
<body class="flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-gray-50 font-sans">
  <%- include("partials/navbar") %>

  <main class="flex-grow flex items-center justify-center py-12 px-6 ">
    <form id="quizForm" method="POST" action="/quiz" class="bg-white w-full max-w-3xl shadow-lg rounded-2xl p-8 space-y-6">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 text-center">Aptitude & Interest Quiz</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-center">Answer honestly — results will recommend a stream after Class 10 and guidance after Class 12.</p>

      
      <div>
        <label class="block text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">1) Which subject(s) do you enjoy most?</label>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2">
          <label class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <input type="checkbox" name="likes[]" value="math"> Mathematics
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <input type="checkbox" name="likes[]" value="physics"> Physics
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <input type="checkbox" name="likes[]" value="chemistry"> Chemistry
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <input type="checkbox" name="likes[]" value="biology"> Biology
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <input type="checkbox" name="likes[]" value="accounts"> Accounts/Business
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <input type="checkbox" name="likes[]" value="history"> Social Studies/History
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <input type="checkbox" name="likes[]" value="arts"> Arts/Design
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      
      <div>
        <label class="block text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">2) What kind of tasks do you prefer?</label>
        <select name="taskType" class="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg" required>
          <option value="">Choose</option>
          <option value="problem">Problem solving / Logic</option>
          <option value="hands">Hands-on / Practical</option>
          <option value="creative">Creative / Design / Writing</option>
          <option value="business">Business / Numbers</option>
          <option value="helping">Helping people / Health</option>
        </select>
      </div>

   
      <div>
        <label class="block text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">3) Which of these describes you best?</label>
        <select name="strength" class="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg" required>
          <option value="">Choose</option>
          <option value="analytical">Analytical / Data-minded</option>
          <option value="practical">Practical / Skilled</option>
          <option value="communicator">Good communication</option>
          <option value="creative">Highly creative</option>
          <option value="leader">Leader / Entrepreneur</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      
      <div>
        <label class="block text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">4) Long-term do you prefer:</label>
        <select name="longTerm" class="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg" required>
          <option value="">Choose</option>
          <option value="job">A steady job quickly</option>
          <option value="degree">Higher degree & research</option>
          <option value="business">Start a business</option>
          <option value="service">Defence / Government service</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      
      <div>
        <label class="block text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">5) Are you open to entrance exams and competitive tests?</label>
        <select name="examOpenness" class="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg" required>
          <option value="">Choose</option>
          <option value="yes">Yes — I will prepare</option>
          <option value="maybe">Maybe — prefer easier paths</option>
          <option value="no">No — prefer skill courses / direct jobs</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      
      <div>
        <label class="block text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">6) Do you already prefer any intermediate group (optional)?</label>
        <select name="prefIntermediate" class="w-full p-3 border rounded-lg">
          <option value="">No preference</option>
          <option value="MPC">MPC (Maths, Physics, Chemistry)</option>
          <option value="BIPC">BiPC (Biology, Physics, Chemistry)</option>
          <option value="Commerce">Commerce</option>
          <option value="Arts">Arts / Humanities</option>
          <option value="Vocational">Vocational / Diploma</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      
      <div class="text-center">
        <button type="submit" class="px-8 py-3 bg-indigo-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow hover:bg-indigo-700 transition">
          Get Recommendations
        </button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </main>

  <%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>
